omni.physx.graph.ImmediateComputeBoundsO.description: Computes overlaps between pairs of axis aligned bounding boxes (broadphase)

omni.physx.graph.ImmediateComputeGeometr.description: Computes bounding boxes for the input geometries (and cache cooking for future intersection tests)
Compute overlaps between geometries (currently supports meshes prims)
Compute penetration depth and direction between geometries (currently supports meshes prims)

omni.physx.graph.ImmediateComputeMeshInt.description: Computes indices of intersecting faces between pairs of Meshes.

omni.physx.graph.ImmediateGenerateGeomet.description: Returns a list of contact points.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQueryOverlapBoxAll.description: Returns a list of prim paths of all colliders that overlap the input box.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQueryOverlapBoxAny.description: Checks whether any colliders overlap the query input box.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQueryOverlapPrimAl.description: Returns a list of prim paths of all colliders that overlap the input Prim.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQueryOverlapPrimAn.description: Checks whether any colliders overlap the query input Prim.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQueryOverlapSphere.description: Returns a list of prim paths of all colliders that overlap the input sphere.
Checks whether any colliders overlap the query input sphere.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQueryRaycastAll.description: Returns a list of prim paths of all colliders that are hit by the input ray.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQueryRaycastAny.description: Returns whether any colliders are hit by the input ray.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQueryRaycastCloses.description: Finds the closest collider that is hit by the input ray.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQuerySweepSphereAl.description: Returns a list of prim paths of all colliders that are hit by the input sweep.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQuerySweepSphereAn.description: Returns whether any colliders are hit by the input sweep.

omni.physx.graph.SceneQuerySweepSphereCl.description: Finds the closest collider that is hit by the input sweep.

omni.physx.graph.OnTriggerCollider.description: Emits an event when a collider enters or leaves the volume of a Trigger.

omni.physx.graph.VehicleGetDriveState.description: Retrieving drive related simulation state of an omni.physx vehicle

omni.physx.graph.VehicleGetWheelState.description: Retrieving wheel related simulation state of an omni.physx vehicle
